      "text": "……はぁ\nあ……いけないいけない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sigh.\nAh… I can’t do this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.9073924224
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "これからは四人で頑張るんだから\nいつまでもため息ばっかりついてちゃダメだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have to work hard with the four of us from now on‚\nso I can’t keep sighing forever.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "四人で成長して……琴乃ちゃんがいつでも\n帰って来れるようにしないと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We need to grow as a four-member group… so that\nKotono-chan can come back anytime!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.3130119015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.6826526483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "よーし、頑張るぞー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ let’s do this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.6826526483,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4671.133693200001,
          "startTime": 24.3537863415
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 24.1037863415
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyo-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 24.3537863415
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、おはよー！\n……あれ、どうかしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ everyone!\n…Huh‚ what’s wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9989855859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃん……おはようございます\n今、このニュース動画が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa-chan… Good morning.\nThis news video…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.4807477794,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "なんのニュース？\n……え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What news?\n…Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.95,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 45.0809973401
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "男性アナウンサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Male",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さあ、本日のエンタメコーナーですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ for today’s entertainment section…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.0809973401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "男性アナウンサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Male",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "驚きの速報が入ってまいりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have some surprising breaking news.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.7476639273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "『長瀬琴乃　どりきゅんの所属事務所に移籍",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Kotono Nagase Transfers to DoriQyun’s Agency.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.1809973401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "月のテンペスト＆星見プロとの決別か』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Has She Parted Ways with Moon Tempest & Hoshimi Prods?”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.8333333492,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "男性アナウンサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Male",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "こちらの情報ですが、どりきゅんの所属事務所の",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This information comes from an announcement by",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.3143299105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "男性アナウンサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Male",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "発表によるものでして、現在詳細を確認中です――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "DoriQyun’s agency‚ and we are currently confirming the details――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.4143298311,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんが……どりきゅんの事務所に入った……？\nど、どういうこと！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan… joined DoriQyun’s agency…?\nWh-What does this mean!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.1333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "そんなの……私にだって分かりませんわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How should… I know?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.6921980224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんは、月ストを脱退こそしたものの\n星見プロに籍を置いていたはずです。なのにこんな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Although Kotono-chan withdrew from Moon Tempest‚\nshe should still be with Hoshimi Prods. But to think this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.392197943,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "強くなって月ストに戻る、って言ってたよね\n琴乃ちゃん……どうしちゃったのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She said she’d get stronger and come back to Moon Tempest.\nKotono-chan… what happened to her?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.8666633606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "こんなニュース、デマに決まってますわよ！\n私は信じませんわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This news must be fake!\nI don’t believe it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.8949708755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "うん……そうだよ。こんなの絶対嘘に決まってる！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… You’re right. This has got to be a lie!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.1631253562,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6803.541310499994,
          "startTime": 108.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんに確認しないと\n……って、あれ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have to check with {user}-san.\n…Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.8333300273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "月ストのグループメッセージに……\n琴乃ちゃんからメッセージが届いています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In Moon Tempest’s group message…\nthere’s a message from Kotono-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.3717194911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 118.4519688609
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "『ごめん。月ストにはもう戻らない』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Sorry. I’m not coming back to Moon Tempest.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.4519688609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "嘘……嘘だよね……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No… It’s a lie‚ right…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.4853021942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、琴乃がグループから抜けましたわよ……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Kotono left the group…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.8662091418,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "メッセージも既読がつかないし……\nダメだ……電話も通じないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no read receipt on the message…\nNo good… I can’t get through on the phone either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.7706739008,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "もしかしたら……私達全員\nブロックされたのかもしれませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Perhaps… all of us\nhave been blocked?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.5183403656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "そんな……なんで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why… Why would she…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.9516737783,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3196.5760072999956,
          "startTime": 146.1482497856
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3396.5759278000005,
          "startTime": 146.3482497061
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな揃ってるか\n……その様子だと、琴乃から連絡がきたんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is everyone here?\n…Judging from your expressions‚ Kotono contacted you‚ huh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.5815830395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_01-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！\n琴乃ちゃんは……どうしちゃったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!\nWhat… happened to Kotono-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.7666633606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
